content.rendered:
As a part of our efforts to succeed in our environmental targets, iPhone 11 not features a energy adapter or EarPods. Please use your current Apple energy adapter and headphones or purchase these equipment individually
Water and mud resistant (2 meters for as much as half-hour, IP68)
Dual-camera system with 12MP Ultra Wide and Wide cameras; Night mode, Portrait mode, and 4K video as much as 60fps
12MP TrueDepth entrance digicam with Portrait mode, 4K video, and Slo-Mo
Face ID for safe authentication and Apple Pay
A13 Bionic chip with third-era Neural Engine
Fast-charge succesful
Wireless charging
iOS with redesigned widgets on the Home display screen, all-new App Library, App Clips and extra
